                        <interp inst="t18360815-name-943" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES PULLING</persName>
                  </hi>. I was outside the shop—my master had such a piece of bacon as this—I believe it to be his—I saw the prisoner take the pork, and she stood over it—I did not see her take the bacon.</p>
